<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 01:47:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>RNA结合蛋白多样性和NLS精氨酸调节富含mRNA的区室中的FUS混合</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/rna-binding-protein-diversity-and-nls-arginines-regulate-fus-mixing-in-mrna-rich-compartments</link><description>瓦伦蒂等人。使用 MT 台式测定来量化细胞中异质成分区室中的 FUS 同型/异型相互作用。他们表明，FUS 与其他 RBP 的异型相互作用，由其疾病相关的 NLS 精心策划，可以独立于核转运蛋白阻止 FUS 相分离。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/rna-binding-protein-diversity-and-nls-arginines-regulate-fus-mixing-in-mrna-rich-compartments.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 01:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/rna-binding-protein-diversity-and-nls-arginines-regulate-fus-mixing-in-mrna-rich-compartments</guid></item><item><title>工程师们创造了 3D 打印的机器鱼，它们可以游泳、玩耍并通过自动充电系统为自己充电。这就是你需要知道的一切</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/engineers-create-3d-printed-robotic-fish-that-swim-play-and-recharge-themselves-through-automated-charging-systems-heres-all-you-need-to-know</link><description>工程师们开发出了模仿真实水生生物的机器鱼，无需维护即可提供水族馆体验。这些微型潜艇由 Arduino 提供动力，并由头顶摄像头和 Raspberry Pi 引导，可以自主导航、交互，甚至返回无线充电站。这项创新有望实现免维护的水生展示，将技术与自然的宁静融为一体，打造出未来派的水族馆。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/engineers-create-3d-printed-robotic-fish-that-swim-play-and-recharge-themselves-through-automated-charging-systems-heres-all-you-need-to-know.avif" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 01:32:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/engineers-create-3d-printed-robotic-fish-that-swim-play-and-recharge-themselves-through-automated-charging-systems-heres-all-you-need-to-know</guid></item><item><title>一种软可穿戴近红外光谱系统，用于检测与睡眠期间类淋巴活动相关的脑水动态</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-soft-wearable-near-infrared-spectroscopy-system-for-detecting-brain-water-dynamics-linked-to-glymphatic-activity-during-sleep</link><description>科学。副词。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-soft-wearable-near-infrared-spectroscopy-system-for-detecting-brain-water-dynamics-linked-to-glymphatic-activity-during-sleep2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 01:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-soft-wearable-near-infrared-spectroscopy-system-for-detecting-brain-water-dynamics-linked-to-glymphatic-activity-during-sleep</guid></item><item><title>时间来自于整个宇宙的运行计算吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/does-time-come-from-the-entire-universe-running-computations</link><description>解释时间的流逝基本上永远是物理学中的一个棘手问题，但物理学家和计算机科学家斯蒂芬·沃尔夫勒姆（Stephen Wolfram）对时间的来源提出了一个激进的建议。他及时与记者 Leah Crane 讨论了他的想法——以及它们对自由意志的意义。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/does-time-come-from-the-entire-universe-running-computations.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 01:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/does-time-come-from-the-entire-universe-running-computations</guid></item><item><title>人类未来五十亿年</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/five-billion-years-into-humanitys-future</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 00:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/five-billion-years-into-humanitys-future</guid></item><item><title>小型晶体管无需极端冷却即可锐化低成本热感相机</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/small-transistor-sharpens-low-cost-thermal-cameras-without-extreme-cooling</link><description>在小型晶体管的帮助下，夏丰年教授领导的研究小组找到了一种方法，可以使一种热成像技术的精确度大大提高。结果是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/small-transistor-sharpens-low-cost-thermal-cameras-without-extreme-cooling2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 00:32:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/small-transistor-sharpens-low-cost-thermal-cameras-without-extreme-cooling</guid></item><item><title>Skydio X10 技术规格</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/skydio-x10-technical-specs</link><description>Skydio 人工智能驱动的自主无人机适用于公共安全无人机作为急救人员 (DFR) 计划、关键基础设施检查、现场安全和防御。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/skydio-x10-technical-specs3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 00:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/skydio-x10-technical-specs</guid></item><item><title>乔治·戴森谈图灵大教堂：荒野是世界的保护</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/george-dyson-on-turings-cathedral-in-wildness-is-the-preservation-of-the-world</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/george-dyson-on-turings-cathedral-in-wildness-is-the-preservation-of-the-world.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 00:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/george-dyson-on-turings-cathedral-in-wildness-is-the-preservation-of-the-world</guid></item><item><title>科学家们释放了水果和坚果与正确肠道微生物搭配的肠道愈合能力</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-unlock-gut-healing-power-of-fruits-and-nuts-paired-with-the-right-gut-microbes</link><description>路易斯维尔大学的研究人员发现了一种天然存在的微生物化合物如何帮助保护肠道并支持炎症性肠病 (IBD) 的未来治疗策略。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-unlock-gut-healing-power-of-fruits-and-nuts-paired-with-the-right-gut-microbes.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 23:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-unlock-gut-healing-power-of-fruits-and-nuts-paired-with-the-right-gut-microbes</guid></item><item><title>弗兰克·维瑟 / ChatGPT</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/frank-visser-chatgpt</link><description>随着欧文·拉斯洛 (Ervin Laszlo) 于 94 岁去世，世界失去了二十世纪和二十一世纪最多产的整体思维倡导者之一。拉斯洛是哲学家、系统理论家、未来学家、音乐会钢琴家和多个国际组织的创始人，他数十年来一直主张人类需要一种新的世界观——一种能够将科学、生态、伦理和灵性整合成一个连贯愿景的世界观。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/frank-visser-chatgpt.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 23:32:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/frank-visser-chatgpt</guid></item></channel></rss>